-luminosity run or at the\nInternational Linear Collider, we can identify the non-minimal Higgs sector\neven without direct discovery of additional Higgs bosons at the LHC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jun 2014 17:36:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Nov 2014 03:11:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
