y discs and exoplanets in binaries, and can be tested with\nfuture observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jun 2014 19:39:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Sep 2014 16:22:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
