ture DM measurements of GRB-associated FRBs could\nprovide a constraint on the physics of NS winds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jun 2014 12:37:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Jul 2014 09:21:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Nov 2014 02:09:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-14"}
